Good Morning Raffaella,

This has been actioned on my end for you this morning and should be reflect=
ed in your account in the next 3 =E2=80=93 5 business days.

I am also working on the timeline for this claim and hope to have an update=
 for you on this next week.  I will be on leave from later today until Wedn=
esday next week, but I do have access to emails during this time so please =
do reach out if there is anything urgent.

Kind Regards
Lance
