<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Good Afternoon Raffaella,<span style=3D"font-size:10=
.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you for your patience,<span class=3D"xapple-co=
nverted-space">&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></s=
pan></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I have completed my review of the outstanding paymen=
ts on your contents claim and arrange payment of the next $5,000 for tempor=
ary accommodation.&nbsp; Please confirm if this (and future temporary accom=
modation payments) can be made into the
 same account as the previous ones. &nbsp;Once I receive confirmation I wil=
l arrange payment urgently, with this usually being processed within 3 =E2=
=80=93 5 business days.&nbsp;<span class=3D"xapple-converted-space">&nbsp;<=
/span><span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I have also noted that you provided costs for vet fe=
es.&nbsp; These would not be able to be reimbursed as the vet fees are not =
covered by the policy if your pet is injured in an accident with a motor ve=
hicle.<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I can see Zach has already advised you that the wate=
r rates would not be able to be reimbursed.<span class=3D"xapple-converted-=
space">&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I also am happy to confirm that future payments for =
temporary accommodation will be acted upon far more promptly, I recommend s=
ending these to costs to the claims email address, and copying me into it a=
s well.&nbsp;<span class=3D"xapple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><span styl=
e=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please let me know if you have any further questions=
.<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
</div>
